  "Definition": [
   {
    "text": "A binyan is a permutation of a ",
    "type": "text"
   },
   {
    "text": "shoresh",
    "type": "global",
    "tokens": [
     {
      "text": "shoresh",
      "type": "text"
     }
    ],
    "targetSubtopic": "Shoresh",
    "targetTopic": "Shoresh",
    "enclosingTopic": "Binyan",
    "enclosingSubtopic": "Definition"
   },
   {
    "text": " in Hebrew and Aramaic that realizes the general meaning of the shoresh into a particular action or quality. A shoresh might have a general meaning of \"holy,\" whereas a particular binyan of that shoresh might mean \"to make something holy,\" or \"to be holy.\"",
    "type": "text"
   }
  ],
  "Seven binyanim": [
   {
    "text": "Both Hebrew and Aramaic have seven binyanim, although they have slightly different names due to the ",
    "type": "text"
   },
   {
    "text": "binyan naming convention",
    "type": "local",
    "tokens": [
     {
      "text": "binyan naming convention",
      "type": "text"
     }
    ],
    "targetSubtopic": "Binyan naming convention",
    "targetTopic": "Binyan",
    "enclosingTopic": "Binyan",
    "enclosingSubtopic": "Seven binyanim"
   },
   {
    "text": ". The binyanim are the simple-active, the simple-passive, the ",
    "type": "text"
   },
   {
    "text": "intensive-active",
    "type": "global",
    "tokens": [
     {
      "text": "intensive-active",
      "type": "text"
     }
    ],
    "targetSubtopic": "Intensive-active binyan",
    "targetTopic": "Intensive-active binyan",
    "enclosingTopic": "Binyan",
    "enclosingSubtopic": "Seven binyanim"
   },
   {
    "text": ", the intensive-passive, the causative-active, the causative-passive, and the reflexive.",
    "type": "text"
   }
  ],
  "Binyan naming convention": [
   {
    "text": "Binyanim in Hebrew and Aramaic are named after the third-person masculine conjugation of the shoresh פעל in that binyan. So, for example, the ",
    "type": "text"
   },
   {
    "text": "intensive-active binyan",
    "type": "global",
    "tokens": [
     {
      "text": "intensive-active binyan",
